<p>The goal of this class will be to to allow for a <code>help</code> option to be passed to any
field, <em>and</em> to turn that <code>help</code> option into a <code>help</code> variable.</p>
<p>First, all form type extensions should extend <code>AbstractTypeExtension</code>:</p>
