<p>When we're done setting things up, whenever <em>any</em> field is transformed into a <code>FormView</code>
object, this method will be called and <em>we</em> will be able to add variables to anything!</p>
<p>Try it: add <code>$view</code> - which represents whatever one field is being setup -
<code>$view-&gt;vars['help']</code> set to <code>TURTLES</code>!</p>
