<p>Just by doing that, you are now allowed to have a <code>help</code> option on any field. It
also means that when <code>buildView()</code> is called, the <code>$options</code> array will have a key
called <code>help</code>. All we need to say is if <code>$options['help']</code>, then set the <code>help</code> variable
to <code>$options['help']</code>:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="f863de26c4">
